---
 CHANGES.md      | 2 ++
 bin/mjob        | 3 ++-
 man/man1/mjob.1 | 6 +++---
 3 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/CHANGES.md b/CHANGES.md
index 179698b..cfce909 100644
--- a/CHANGES.md
+++ b/CHANGES.md
@@ -2,6 +2,8 @@
 
 ## not yet released
 
+- joyent/node-manta#343 Add `mjob wait` as an alias to `mjob watch`.
+
 ## 5.1.1
 
 - joyent/node-manta#315 document mlogin session termination conditions
diff --git a/bin/mjob b/bin/mjob
index b8196de..c3bfe4f 100755
